title: SwifTEA: Are You A March 4th Believer?
description:
SwiftTok is ablaze with theories about March 4th... Why are we certain that there are clues pointing to this day? And are we once again just clowning? We do a deep dive into these latest theories!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? Let us know! There are lots of ways to reach us!
